msgid "gray mass"
msgid_plural "gray mass"
msgstr[0] "灰色團塊"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "Gelatinous track"
msgid_plural "Gelatinous tracks"
msgstr[0] "膠狀履帶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Gelatinous track'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A set of continuous, interlocking tracks made out of blob.  They can be used"
" in place of wheels, and provide good traction and off-road performance."
msgstr "一套由粘液團製成的連續互鎖履帶。它們可替代車輪使用，提供良好的牽引力和越野性能。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "Oozing track"
msgid_plural "Oozing tracks"
msgstr[0] "滲流履帶"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "Gray track"
msgid_plural "Gray tracks"
msgstr[0] "灰色履帶"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "biting blob"
msgid_plural "biting blobs"
msgstr[0] "噬咬粘液團"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'biting blob'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel shooter'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'snapping ooze'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "A living blob, transformed into a heavy vehicle weapon."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，被改造成重型載具武器。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "gel shooter"
msgid_plural "gel shooters"
msgstr[0] "凝膠發射器"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "frost lancer"
msgid_plural "frost lancers"
msgstr[0] "霜凍長槍"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frost lancer'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living blob, existing in a super-cooled state and transformed into a heavy"
" vehicle weapon."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，處於超冷狀態，並被改造成重型載具武器。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "ice ram"
msgstr "冰霜衝角"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ice ram'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living blob, existing in a super-cooled state.  It will absorb damage in a"
" vehicle collision and deliver additional damage to the other object in the "
"collision.  It should be mounted on the edge of the vehicle, preferably the "
"front."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，處於超冷狀態。它會在載具碰撞時吸收傷害，並對碰撞的另一物體造成額外傷害。應安裝在載具邊緣，最好是前部。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "ice pack"
msgstr "冰霜包"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ice pack'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living blob, existing in a super-cooled state.  It will keep items stored "
"in it cold, reducing the speed at which food and drink rots."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，處於超冷狀態。它能保持儲存其中的物品低溫，減緩食物和飲料的腐敗速度。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "icy windshield"
msgstr "冰霜擋風玻璃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'icy windshield'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living blob, existing in a super-cooled state.  It is transparent, and can"
" be used to see out of the vehicle."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，處於超冷狀態。它是透明的，可用於觀察載具外部。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "snow slider"
msgstr "雪地滑板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'snow slider'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "A living blob, existing in a super-cooled state.  It acts as a wheel."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，處於超冷狀態。它充當車輪使用。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "icy sea skimmer"
msgstr "冰霜海面滑行器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'icy sea skimmer'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living blob, existing in a super-cooled state.  It acts as a boat hull."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，處於超冷狀態。它充當船體使用。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "snapping ooze"
msgid_plural "snapping oozes"
msgstr[0] "噬咬軟泥"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel lamp"
msgstr "凝膠燈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel lamp'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living, glowing blob.  It produces a bright light that illuminates a "
"narrow cone outside the vehicle when turned on.  During installation, you "
"can choose what direction to point the light, so multiple gel lamps can "
"illuminate the sides or rear, as well as the front."
msgstr ""
"一個活體發光凝膠團。開啟時，它會產生明亮的光線，照亮載具外部一個狹窄的錐形區域。安裝時，可以選擇光照方向，因此多個凝膠燈可以照亮側面或後方，以及前方。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "directed gel lamp"
msgstr "定向凝膠燈"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel retriever"
msgstr "凝膠回收器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel retriever'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray retriever'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ooze retriever'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living blob, formed to act as a scoop.  Use the vehicle controls to turn "
"it on or off.  When turned on, it will scoop up any loose items that it "
"travels over, putting them into the vehicle's storage."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，被塑造成剷鬥形狀。使用載具控制裝置開啟或關閉它。開啟時，它會剷起經過的任何鬆散物品，並將其放入載具的存儲空間中。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel harness"
msgstr "凝膠安全帶"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel harness'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray harness'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ooze harness'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "A living blob, reformed as a belt and attached to a seat."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，被重塑為安全帶並連接到座椅上。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "capsule (10L)"
msgstr "膠囊（10升）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'capsule (10L)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cocoon (30L)'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pod (20L)'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living blob, formed into a storage space for holding liquids.  If filled "
"with the appropriate fuel for the vehicle's engine, the engine will "
"automatically draw fuel from the tank when the engine is on.  If filled with"
" water, you can access the water from a water faucet, if one is installed in"
" the vehicle.  You can also use a rubber hose to siphon liquids out of a "
"tank."
msgstr ""
"一個活體凝膠團，被塑造成儲存液體的空間。如果填充了載具發動機的適當燃料，發動機開啟時會自動從油箱中抽取燃料。如果填充了水，可以從載具中安裝的水龍頭（如果已安裝）取水。也可以使用橡膠軟管從油箱中虹吸液體。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel tank (60L)"
msgstr "凝膠油箱（60升）"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel framework"
msgstr "凝膠框架"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel framework'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray frame'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ooze chassis'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living blob, shaped to provide attachment points for other blobs.  Other "
"vehicle components and blobs can be mounted on it.  If all the frames and "
"components of a vehicle are foldable or made from blobs, the vehicle can be "
"folding into a small package and picked up as a normal item."
msgstr ""
"一個活體凝膠團，被塑造成提供其他凝膠團的附著點。其他載具組件和凝膠團可以安裝在其上。如果載具的所有框架和組件都是可摺疊的或由凝膠團製成，則載具可以摺疊成一個小包裹，並作為普通物品拾取。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel reinforcement"
msgstr "凝膠強化板"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel reinforcement'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray reinforcement'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ooze reinforcement'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "A living blob, acting as armor plate."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，充當裝甲板。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel roof"
msgstr "凝膠車頂"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel roof'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray roof'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ooze roof'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "A living blob, placed as roof."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，用作屋頂。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel seat"
msgstr "凝膠座椅"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel seat'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray seat'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ooze seat'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "A living blob, formed into a comfy couch.  You can sit here."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，塑造成舒適的沙發。你可以坐在這裡。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel receptacle"
msgstr "凝膠容器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel receptacle'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray receptacle'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ooze receptacle'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "A living blob, shaped into a cargo space."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，塑造成貨物空間。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel pouch (under)"
msgstr "凝膠袋（下方）"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgid "gelatinous wheel"
msgid_plural "gelatinous wheels"
msgstr[0] "凝膠輪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gelatinous wheel'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray wheel'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "A living blob.  It acts as a wheel."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團。它充當車輪。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel walkway"
msgstr "凝膠走道"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel walkway'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray walkway'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ooze walkway'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "A living blob, formed into a walkway."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，塑造成走道。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel panel"
msgstr "凝膠面板"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel hatch"
msgstr "凝膠艙口"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel hatch'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gray hatch'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ooze hatch'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living blob, acting as a door.  Has a transparent patch so you can see out"
" of it, even when closed."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，充當門。有一個透明區域，即使關閉時也能看到外面。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "opaque gel hatch"
msgstr "不透明凝膠艙口"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'opaque gel hatch'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'opaque gray hatch'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'opaque ooze hatch'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living blob, acting as a door.  Entirely opaque so you can't see through "
"it when closed."
msgstr "一個活體凝膠團，充當門。完全不透明，關閉時無法看透。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel battery"
msgstr "凝膠電池"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel battery'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living, glowing blob.  Having been filled with electrical power, it stores"
" that power and can release it to power other parts of the vehicle, allowing"
" it to act as a storage battery."
msgstr "一個活體發光凝膠團。充滿電能後，它儲存能量並可以釋放以驅動車輛的其他部分，使其充當蓄電池。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel battery (under)"
msgstr "凝膠電池（下方）"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "gel generator"
msgstr "凝膠發電機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gel generator'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A living, glowing blob.  It consumes blob feed and produces electrical "
"power, allowing it to be used as a reactor.  It also glows, and can be "
"turned on to illuminate several squares inside the vehicle."
msgstr "一個活體發光凝膠團。它消耗凝膠飼料併產生電能，可用作反應堆。它還會發光，開啟時可以照亮車輛內的幾個方格。"

