#. ~ Description for {'str': 'amorphous core'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "An amorphous mass, the living heart and brain of a blob vehicle."
msgstr "一團不定形物質，是黏液載具的活體心臟與大腦。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid "inert core"
msgstr "惰性核心"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'inert core'}
#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json
msgid ""
"A sleeping amorphous core, acting as a rotating, universal mount for a "
"weapon.  If your hands are empty, you can stand next to a tentacle and "
"'f'ire the weapon by selecting the tile."
msgstr "一個沉睡的不定形核心，作為武器的旋轉式通用支架。若你雙手空空，可站在觸手旁，通過選擇對應格子按'f'鍵開火使用武器。"

#: .\blaze_blob_parts.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
