#. ~ Description for Blazemod - Vehicle Additions Pack
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Gigantic vehicle parts additions mod. Adds lots of regular along with blob "
"vehicle parts which includes new custom turrets, engines along with other "
"vehicle parts, which are craftable."
msgstr "龐大的載具部件附加模組。添加了大量常規部件以及粘液載具部件，包括新的定製炮塔、引擎以及其他可製作的載具部件。"

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Agh, to See the Spiral in such a Distorted Shape!  Manipulated for its "
"Vortex motion!  Its Perpetual Grace!  Its beauty Tarnished…\""
msgstr "\"啊，竟見螺旋以如此扭曲之形！被操縱以取其渦流之動！其永恆之優雅！其美被玷汙……\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"My friend died, but at least I made her into a blob turret.\""
msgstr "\"我的朋友死了，但至少我把她做成了粘液炮塔。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"I have this laser cannon turret on my shopping cart.  I push it around and"
" everything dies.  I think I'm gonna toss it in the lake-- this just isn't "
"fair anymore.\""
msgstr "\"我的購物車上裝了一門激光炮塔。我推著它到處走，所有東西都死了。我想我要把它扔進湖裡——這已經不公平了。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Day 40.  Controls broken-- car's magic reactor makes it goes inexorably "
"forward.  Giant rollers on front demolish forest.  Maine, here I come.\""
msgstr "\"第40天。控制失靈——車的魔法反應堆讓它不可阻擋地向前衝。前部的巨型滾輪摧毀了森林。緬因州，我來了。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"my car is a diamond in the rough… literally\""
msgstr "\"我的車是塊未經雕琢的鑽石……字面意思上\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"M249 TURRET NODDED.  IS TURRET ALIVE?  FINALLY, SOMEBODY TO TALK TO!\""
msgstr "\"M249炮塔點頭了。炮塔是活的嗎？終於有人可以說話了！\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"Added so many things to my taxi that it went a-blaze.  Whoops.\""
msgstr "\"給我的出租車加了太多東西，結果它著火了。哎呀。\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"If I put one cargo dimension into another cargo dimension, does the "
"universe end?\""
msgstr "\"如果我把一個貨運用次元空間放進另一個貨運用次元空間裡，宇宙會終結嗎？\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid "\"one day, i will be part of car, too\""
msgstr "\"總有一天，我也會成為車的一部分\""

#: .\snippets.json
msgid ""
"\"Putta little bitta dynamite and halfa landmine in an old soda can…  WHAM!"
"  You goin' somewhere.\""
msgstr "\"往舊汽水罐裡塞點炸藥和半顆地雷……轟！你就飛上天了。\""

