" trigger it.  Intended to be fired from a specialized launcher.  This one is"
" designed to douse a large area with deadly flames."
msgstr "一種簡易爆炸裝置，由裝滿有效載荷材料和觸發裝置的容器構成。設計用於從專用發射器發射。此型號旨在向大範圍區域噴灑致命火焰。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "fragmentation canister"
msgid_plural "fragmentation canisters"
msgstr[0] "破片罐"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fragmentation canister'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"An IED composed of a container filled with a payload material and a means to"
" trigger it.  Intended to be fired from a specialized launcher.  This one is"
" designed to spray the immediate area with deadly shrapnel."
msgstr "一種簡易爆炸裝置，由裝滿有效載荷材料和觸發裝置的容器構成。設計用於從專用發射器發射。此型號旨在向周圍區域噴灑致命破片。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "modified mininuke"
msgid_plural "modified mininukes"
msgstr[0] "改裝微型核彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'modified mininuke'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A heavy modified handheld nuclear device.  Intended to be fired from a "
"specialized launcher, its case has been cut down and it has been rigged to "
"explode on impact.  While it is now somewhat lighter than before, it can no "
"longer be triggered manually."
msgstr "一款經過重度改裝的便攜式核裝置。設計用於從專用發射器發射，其外殼已被削減，並改裝為撞擊時爆炸。雖然現在比之前輕了一些，但無法再手動觸發。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'harpoon'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A large spear carved from wood.  This was fashioned specifically to be fired"
" from a compatible weapon; thus unsuitable for melee combat."
msgstr "一根用木頭雕刻而成的大型長矛。這是專門為從兼容武器發射而製作的；因此不適合近戰。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "IED on a bolt"
msgid_plural "IED on a bolts"
msgstr[0] "弩箭簡易爆炸裝置"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "nova bolt"
msgid_plural "nova bolts"
msgstr[0] "新星弩箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nova bolt'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"An IED composed of a sealed container filled with a payload material affixed"
" to the end of a large ballista bolt.  Intended to be fired from a "
"specialized launcher.  Carries a substantial explosive payload."
msgstr "一種簡易爆炸裝置，由裝滿有效載荷材料的密封容器固定在大型弩箭末端構成。設計用於從專用發射器發射。攜帶大量爆炸性有效載荷。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "supernova bolt"
msgid_plural "supernova bolts"
msgstr[0] "超新星弩箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'supernova bolt'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"An IED composed of a sealed container filled with a payload material affixed"
" to the end of a large ballista bolt.  Intended to be fired from a "
"specialized launcher.  Carries a very substantial explosive payload."
msgstr "一種簡易爆炸裝置，由裝滿有效載荷材料的密封容器固定在大型弩箭末端構成。設計用於從專用發射器發射。攜帶巨量爆炸性有效載荷。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "searing bolt"
msgid_plural "searing bolts"
msgstr[0] "灼熱弩箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'searing bolt'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"An IED composed of a container filled with a payload material affixed to the"
" end of a large ballista bolt.  Intended to be fired from a specialized "
"launcher.  This one is designed to douse a small area with deadly flames."
msgstr "一種簡易爆炸裝置，由裝滿有效載荷材料的容器固定在大型弩箭末端構成。設計用於從專用發射器發射。此型號旨在向小範圍區域噴灑致命火焰。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "napalm bolt"
msgid_plural "napalm bolts"
msgstr[0] "凝固汽油弩箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'napalm bolt'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"An IED composed of a container filled with a payload material affixed to the"
" end of a large ballista bolt.  Intended to be fired from a specialized "
"launcher.  This one is designed to douse a large area with deadly flames."
msgstr "一種簡易爆炸裝置，由裝滿有效載荷材料的容器固定在大型弩箭末端構成。設計用於從專用發射器發射。此型號旨在向大範圍區域噴灑致命火焰。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "shatter bolt"
msgid_plural "shatter bolts"
msgstr[0] "碎裂弩箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shatter bolt'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"An IED composed of a container filled with a payload material affixed to the"
" end of a large ballista bolt.  Intended to be fired from a specialized "
"launcher.  This one is designed to spray the immediate area with deadly "
"shrapnel."
msgstr "一種簡易爆炸裝置，由裝滿有效載荷材料的容器固定在大型弩箭末端構成。設計用於從專用發射器發射。此型號旨在向周圍區域噴灑致命破片。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "steel ballista bolt"
msgid_plural "steel ballista bolts"
msgstr[0] "鋼製弩箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'steel ballista bolt'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A long shaft carved from wood ending in a tip of sharpened metal.  It's "
"quite heavy, capable of dealing large amounts of damage, but isn't "
"particularly accurate.  Stands a good chance of remaining intact once fired."
msgstr "一根木製長杆，末端為鋒利的金屬尖頭。它相當沉重，能造成大量傷害，但準頭不佳。發射後有較大幾率保持完好。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "nuclear bolt"
msgid_plural "nuclear bolts"
msgstr[0] "核能弩箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'nuclear bolt'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A heavy modified handheld nuclear device affixed to the end of a large "
"ballista bolt.  Its case has been cut down and it has been rigged to explode"
" on impact.  It can no longer be triggered manually."
msgstr "一支經過重度改裝的手持核裝置，固定在一根大型弩箭的末端。其外殼已被削減，並改裝為撞擊引爆。無法再手動觸發。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "wood ballista bolt"
msgid_plural "wood ballista bolts"
msgstr[0] "木質弩箭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wood ballista bolt'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A sharpened bolt carved from wood.  It's fairly heavy, capable of dealing "
"large amounts of damage, but isn't particularly accurate.  Stands a good "
"chance of remaining intact once fired."
msgstr "一根由木材雕刻而成的鋒利弩箭。相當沉重，能造成大量傷害，但精度不高。發射後有很大幾率保持完好。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "lead ball"
msgid_plural "lead balls"
msgstr[0] "鉛球"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'lead ball'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A heavy lead ball about 8cm in diameter.  Could pack quite a bit of a punch "
"if you had something to launch it."
msgstr "一個直徑約8釐米的沉重鉛球。如果有東西能發射它，威力會相當可觀。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "serrated disc"
msgid_plural "serrated discs"
msgstr[0] "鋸齒圓盤"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'serrated disc'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A metal disc surrounded by serrated edges.  It's as menacing as it sounds."
msgstr "一個邊緣佈滿鋸齒的金屬圓盤。聽起來就令人膽寒。"

#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "metal fragment"
msgid_plural "metal fragments"
msgstr[0] "金屬碎片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'metal fragment'}
#: .\items\ammo\blaze_ammo.json
msgid "Small slivers of metal.  Can't see much use for them."
msgstr "細小的金屬碎片。看不出有什麼大用處。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "storm bolter"
msgid_plural "storm bolters"
msgstr[0] "風暴弩炮"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"This pneumatic bolt thrower has been greatly enhanced, allowing multiple "
"bolts to be launched accurately and in quick succession.  It requires a "
"support of some sort in order to be operated."
msgstr "這把氣動弩炮經過大幅增強，能夠快速連續地精準發射多支弩箭。它需要某種支撐才能操作。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "slingshot cannon"
msgid_plural "slingshot cannons"
msgstr[0] "彈弓加農炮"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"Essentially several long drawstrings held by two long, reinforced sides and "
"a mechanism attached to a crank to draw and fire it.  It's deceptively "
"powerful and surprisingly accurate, but far too large to be used without "
"some sort of stable platform."
msgstr "本質上是由兩根加固長臂固定的多根長拉繩，以及一個連接曲柄用於拉弦和發射的機構。它威力驚人且出奇地精準，但體積過大，沒有穩定平臺無法使用。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "lacerator"
msgid_plural "lacerators"
msgstr[0] "撕裂者"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"This weapon launches serrated metal disks at nearby enemies.  It draws its "
"power from a vehicle's engines, and thus must be mounted on such in order to"
" be operated."
msgstr "這種武器向附近的敵人發射鋸齒金屬圓盤。它從車輛的引擎獲取動力，因此必須安裝在車輛上才能操作。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json .\items\vehicle\blaze_blob.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "pistol"
msgstr "手槍"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "rotary cannon"
msgid_plural "rotary cannons"
msgstr[0] "轉輪加農炮"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"This fearsome weapon sports 3 barrels in a cyclic configuration.  A "
"specialized mechanism loads the otherwise troublesome rounds; allowing it to"
" be fired in quick succession.  However, this renders it incredibly "
"unwieldy, and it must be mounted on a support structure in order to be "
"fired."
msgstr ""
"這種可怕的武器採用三管循環配置。一個專門的機構裝填原本棘手的彈藥，使其能夠快速連續射擊。然而，這也使其極其笨重，必須安裝在支撐結構上才能開火。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "laser cannon"
msgid_plural "laser cannons"
msgstr[0] "激光加農炮"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"This enhanced laser cannon sacrifices efficiency for destructive power.  The"
" increased power requirements require a significant power source and the "
"size of the firing mechanism also requires support."
msgstr "這種增強型激光加農炮犧牲了效率以換取破壞力。增加的能量需求需要強大的電源，而發射機構的大小也需要支撐。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "pulse laser"
msgid_plural "pulse lasers"
msgstr[0] "脈衝激光器"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"Augmented damage capability and rapid bursts make this a powerful weapon.  "
"The increased power requirements require a significant power source and the "
"firing mechanism also requires a specialized chassis."
msgstr "增強的傷害能力和快速連發使其成為一種強大的武器。增加的能量需求需要強大的電源，而發射機構也需要專門的底盤。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "turbolaser cannon"
msgid_plural "turbolaser cannons"
msgstr[0] "渦輪激光加農炮"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"With an augmented emitter and capacitor, this mounted laser is capable of "
"superheating most materials to the point of exploding.  The firing mechanism"
" also requires the services of a specialized chassis, and one must be wary "
"of the prodigious power needs of such a weapon."
msgstr "憑藉增強的發射器和電容器，這種架設式激光器能夠將大多數材料加熱到爆炸的程度。發射機構也需要專門的底盤，並且必須警惕這種武器巨大的能量需求。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "perforator"
msgid_plural "perforators"
msgstr[0] "穿孔者"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A coilgun with improved electromagnetic circuits to be able to propel a "
"metallic projectile at high speed and with great accuracy.  Capable of "
"piercing armor with little issue, though the projectile itself lacks damage "
"due to its small size.  It must be mounted on a specialized chassis in order"
" to be fired."
msgstr ""
"一種改進了電磁電路的線圈炮，能夠高速且精準地發射金屬彈丸。能夠輕鬆穿透裝甲，但由於彈丸體積小，其本身傷害有限。必須安裝在專門的底盤上才能發射。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "needler"
msgid_plural "needlers"
msgstr[0] "針刺槍"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"This improved nailgun features a special firing mechanism that is set to "
"fire a spread of up to 5 nails at once; sure to drop the hammer on its "
"unfortunate targets.  However, these features render it incredibly unwieldy,"
" and it must be mounted on a supporting frame in order to be fired."
msgstr ""
"這種改進型射釘槍配備了一個特殊的發射機構，可以一次發射最多5枚釘子，足以讓不幸的目標吃盡苦頭。然而，這些特性使其極其笨重，必須安裝在支撐架上才能發射。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "hypervelocity driver"
msgid_plural "hypervelocity drivers"
msgstr[0] "超高速驅動器"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A single-shot, electrically propelled, steel rail launcher.  The powerful, "
"and frankly dangerous, improvements made to the power systems of this weapon"
" is capable imbuing a massive charge into a single-rail; so much that it "
"often shatters into deadly fragments on impact.  It's capabilities are "
"limited by its prodigious power requirements however, and its large size "
"necessitates an appropriately-equipped vehicle."
msgstr ""
"一種單發、電力推進的鋼軌發射器。對其動力系統進行的強大且相當危險的改進，能夠將巨大的電荷注入單根軌道；以至於彈丸在撞擊時常常會碎裂成致命的碎片。然而，其能力受到巨大能量需求的限制，龐大的體積也需要配備相應設備的車輛。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "ripper"
msgid_plural "rippers"
msgstr[0] "撕裂者"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"This menacing weapon rapidly launches bladed disks that rips through enemies"
" with devastating effect.  It draws its power from a vehicle's engines, and "
"thus must be mounted on such in order to be operated."
msgstr "這種威脅性武器能快速發射帶刃圓盤，以毀滅性效果撕裂敵人。它從車輛引擎汲取動力，因此必須安裝在車輛上才能操作。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "rotary speargun"
msgid_plural "rotary spearguns"
msgstr[0] "旋轉魚叉槍"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"This pneumatic speargun features a revolving barrel behind its launcher, "
"allowing projectiles to be rapidly loaded and fired.    However, the weight "
"requires an external support measure."
msgstr "這款氣動魚叉槍在發射器後方設有旋轉槍管，可快速裝填併發射彈丸。然而，其重量需要外部支撐措施。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "scorpion ballista"
msgid_plural "scorpion ballistas"
msgstr[0] "蠍弩"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A massive tension-operated crossbow.  The hand-crank allows one to draw it "
"without the need for heavy labor.  It's far too massive to be used on foot, "
"and thus needs to be mounted on a vehicle in order to be operated."
msgstr "一把巨大的張力驅動弩。手搖曲柄使其無需重體力即可上弦。它過於龐大，無法徒步使用，因此需要安裝在車輛上才能操作。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "splintergun"
msgid_plural "splinterguns"
msgstr[0] "碎片槍"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A heavily modified coilgun that fires tiny fragments of metal at high speeds"
" extremely quickly.  The resulting barrage is highly inaccurate, but can "
"turn unarmored targets into pulp.  It must be mounted on a specialized "
"chassis in order to be fired."
msgstr "一款經過大幅改裝的線圈槍，能以極快速度高速發射微小金屬碎片。其彈幕極不精準，但能將無裝甲目標打成肉泥。必須安裝在專用底盤上才能發射。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "harpoon gun"
msgid_plural "harpoon guns"
msgstr[0] "捕鯨槍"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A tension-operated speargun.  A hand-crank lets one draw the strings "
"quickly, but it's too unwieldy to handle without a support of some sort."
msgstr "一把張力驅動的魚叉槍。手搖曲柄可快速拉緊弓弦，但若無某種支撐，它過於笨重難以手持。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "Tesla cannon"
msgid_plural "Tesla cannons"
msgstr[0] "特斯拉炮"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"This alteration of the Chain Lightning bionic fires artificial lightning "
"bolts that arc to nearby enemies.  It must be attached to a large power "
"source, but it allows for much more powerful bolts."
msgstr "這是對“連鎖閃電”仿生體的改造，可發射人工閃電束，電弧會跳躍至附近敵人。它必須連接大型電源，但能釋放更強大的閃電束。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid "avalanche rifle"
msgid_plural "avalanche rifles"
msgstr[0] "雪崩步槍"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons.json
msgid ""
"This pneumatic assault rifle has been greatly enhanced, firing projectiles "
"faster and with higher velocity.  However, these features render it "
"incredibly unwieldy, and it must be mounted on a supporting platform in "
"order to be fired."
msgstr "這款氣動突擊步槍經過大幅增強，射彈更快、初速更高。然而，這些特性使其極其笨重，必須安裝在支撐平臺上才能發射。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid ""
"This heavy weapon is mounted on a turret, and can be fired from your vehicle"
" controls."
msgstr "這款重型武器安裝在炮塔上，可通過車輛控制裝置發射。"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
msgid "manual storm bolter"
msgstr "手動風暴爆彈槍"

#: .\items\guns\blaze_weapons_parts.json
